graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-1295]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    NotebookController -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22.0+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OPTIONAL]
    NotebookController -.->|traffic mgmt| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>USE_ISTIO=true]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|creates CRDs| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway<br/>VirtualService CRDs<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Dashboard[Kubeflow Dashboard] -->|UI management| NotebookController

    %% Kubernetes Core Components
    NotebookController -->|API operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    K8sAPI -->|schedules| Kubelet[Kubelet]
    Kubelet -->|manages| NotebookPods[Notebook Pods<br/>Jupyter Servers]

    %% Certificate Management (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>webhook TLS]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    NotebookPods -->|package mgmt| Internet[Internet<br/>PyPI/Conda/Container Registries]
    NotebookPods -.->|data access| Storage[Storage Backends<br/>S3/PVC/NFS]

    %% Monitoring Flow
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes :8080| NotebookController

    %% Culling Integration
    NotebookController -->|queries :8888| NotebookPods

